{"tid":315624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑 :【別讓董建華跑了】","createTime":"2017-07-10T07:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T11:04:30.000Z","uid":30561,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b52f902f7e76ffac49870bd52878744990fb033","tid":315624,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:11:01.000Z","msg":"陶傑 :【別讓董建華跑了】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/photos/a.288915521180978.65927.272574169481780/1564871113585406/?type=1&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftokit.channel%2Fphotos%2Fa.288915521180978.65927.272574169481780%2F1564871113585406%2F%3Ftype%3D1%26theater&d=HAPa5dXP9WoaLJ2U5vHgdZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=540fa0d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/photos/a.288915521180978.65927.272574169481780/1564871113585406/?type=1&amp;theater</a> <br />\n【別讓董建華跑了】 <br />\n梁振英不斷聲稱，中國「一帶一路」，香港有運行，並自稱會為香港貢獻「一帶一路」而親自督導。 <br />\n據說房地產泡沫隨時爆，應該趕投注「一帶一路」戰略產業。香港若參與「一帶一路」，第一個發達，當然不是住劏房的香港基層市民，而是「海上絲綢之路」的航運業大亨。 <br />\n但是，連航運老闆董建華都帶頭沽售「東方」航運，率領其家族退出「一帶一路」第一商機，亦即向習近平及「中華民族偉大復興」投下不信任票。 <br />\n急腳撤資套現時，老董對腳出得快、狠、準，不見有「腳痛」之患。 <br />\n「一帶一路」到底如何帶挈香港？連老董見到梁振英之「督導」，都即時逆向套現，不知是梁特的「氣場」猛，還是老董不懵，越老越了解中國？"},{"pid":"7da174e99914377a92bdf421b9160d728471bd9e","tid":315624,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc148c9d6b66f11da1cf20093ef60b29c6653efe","tid":315624,"uid":7206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:41:05.000Z","msg":"老董咁老梗係唔想晚節不保啦，套現確保榮華富貴先係正路，愛國？梗係愛錢啦戇撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a624ec764b5d9436e1e8e6f98e85df779e8c74","tid":315624,"uid":53687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:47:52.000Z","msg":"剩係個標題都抽乾晒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm